race.comment: ALL TOO FOXY (9) made a strong late bid only to just miss as favourite last start at Murwillumbah. No tougher this time and is cherry-ripe fitness now. Leading player. SIGNATURE TART (6) resumes and has filled a minor placing at both first-up runs. Not seen at public trials but draws well and is expected to play a role. SUPERSTITIOUS (3) returns and has been readied with a nice trial win on the Gold Coast. Gets a key booking in Mallyon, who reunites and is unbeaten aboard. Have to take seriously. ZOSMA (4) recorded a gutsy maiden victory last time at Grafton. Still lightly raced and can keep the ball rolling at each-way odds.
